    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770205854</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">The Drawings of Annibale Carracci</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Zeichnungen von Annibale Carracci</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les schémas d'Annibale Carracci</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Os desenhos de Annibale Carracci</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Le illustrazioni di Annibale Carracci</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τα σχέδια Annibale Carracci</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Los gráficos de Annibale Carracci</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">explores the first exhibition devoted solely to the powerful and evocative drawings of Annibale Carracci (1560-1609). From his early experiments with naturalism to his late, almost abstract, style, Annibale revolutionized our way of looking at the world around us and at the art of the past.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Arts</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">erforscht die erste Ausstellung, die nur den 
leistungsfähigen und evocative Zeichnungen von Annibale Carracci 
(1560-1609) gewidmet wird. Von seiner revolutionierten frühe 
Experimente mit Naturalismus zu seinem spät, fast Auszug, Art, 
Annibale unsere Methode des Betrachtens der Welt um uns und der kunst 
der Vergangenheit.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">explore la première exposition consacrée 
seulement aux schémas puissants et évocateurs d'Annibale Carracci 
(1560-1609). Du sien les expériences tôt avec le naturalisme 
au sien tard, presque abstrait, modèle, Annibale ont révolutionné 
notre voie de regarder le monde autour de nous et l'art du passé.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">explora o primeiro exhibition devotado unicamente 
aos desenhos poderosos e evocative de Annibale Carracci (1560-1609). 
De his as experiências adiantadas com naturalism a his tarde, 
quase sumário, estilo, Annibale revolutionized nossa maneira de olhar
o mundo em torno de nós e na arte do passado.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">esplora la prima mostra dedicata solamente alle 
illustrazioni potenti ed evocative di Annibale Carracci (1560-1609). 
Da suo gli esperimenti iniziali con naturalism a suo in ritardo,
quasi estratto, lo stile, Annibale hanno rivoluzionato il nostro modo 
di osservare il mondo intorno noi e l'arte dell'esperienza.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">ερευνά την πρώτη έκθεση που αφιερώνεται απλώς στα 
ισχυρά και προκαλούντα σχέδια Annibale Carracci 
(1560-1609). Από τα πρόωρα πειράματά του με το 
νατουραλισμό σε πρόσφατά του, σχεδόν αφηρημένος, το ύφος, 
Annibale ξεσήκωσε τον τρόπο μας στον κόσμο γύρω από μας και 
την τέχνη του παρελθόντος.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">explora la primera exposición dedicada solamente 
a los gráficos de gran alcance y evocadores de Annibale Carracci 
(1560-1609). La suya los experimentos tempranos con naturalism 
el suyo tarde, casi extracto, estilo, Annibale revolucionaron nuestra 
manera de mirar el mundo alrededor de nosotros y el arte del pasado.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Künste</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Arts</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Artes</string>
          </keyword>
